README.md
     1→# MCPHost 🤖
     3→A CLI host application that enables Large Language Models (LLMs) to interact with external tools through the Model Context Protocol (MCP). Currently supports Claude, OpenAI, Google Gemini, and Ollama models.
     4→
     5→Discuss the Project on [Discord](https://discord.gg/RqSS2NQVsY)
