contribute/contribute.md
     1→# Contribute README
     2→Thanks for your contribution, you can follow these step to run this repo and debug it.
     3→## Run demo
     4→1. clone this repo to your work dir.
     5→    ```bash
     6→    git clone https://github.com/mark3labs/mcphost.git
     7→    ```
     8→
     9→2. enter the `contribute` dir.
    10→    ```bash
    11→    cd mcphost/contribute
    12→    ```
    13→
    14→3. run `build.sh` to build your binary file.
    15→   ```bash
    16→      ./build.sh
    17→   ```
    18→
    19→4. open `boost.sh` file and fill your model info in.
    20→   ```bash
    21→      cat boost.sh
    22→      vi boost.sh
    23→   ```
    24→
      →…
    30→## Contribute your code
    31→just write your code and push it.

