   136→## Environment Variables
   138→All CLI environment variables work with the SDK:
   139→
   140→- `MCPHOST_MODEL` - Override model
   141→- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - Anthropic API key
   142→- `OPENAI_API_KEY` - OpenAI API key
   143→- `GEMINI_API_KEY` - Google API key
   144→- etc.
